Packages 
Package Description
client
A package for client-related socket classes.
function
A package for custom FunctionalInterface used in the application.
game
A package for game classes available for client usage.
game.actions
A package for game movement enums.
game.internal.assets
A package for global asset manager classes.
game.internal.entities
A package for game entities.
gui
A package for classes related to the application GUI.
gui.client
A package for classes related to the application client GUI.
gui.components
A package for classes shared between host and client GUIs.
gui.host
A package for classes related to the application host GUI.
loader
A package for classes related to the application object loader.
server
A package for classes related to the application host server.
util
A package for utility classes.
